  <brief_title>Control of Emergence Blood Pressure During Craniotomy for Tumor Surgery Between Labetolol and Diltiazem</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Comparative Study in the Control of Emergence Blood Pressure During Craniotomy for Tumor Surgery Between Labetolol (Avexa) and Diltiazem</official_title>
  <sponsors>
