  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  patients who scheduled for craniotomy for tomor removal

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  allergic to labetalol or diltiazem

          -  Bradycardia &lt; 60 beat/min

          -  Second or third degree heart block

          -  Severe asthma or severe COPD

          -  Brain stem tumor
      </textblock>
